            <paragraph>Font descent (number of pixels below the baseline). If set to <literal>0</literal>, half of the character height is used.</paragraph>
            <transition classes="classref-item-separator"></transition>
            <target refid="class-resourceimporterimagefont-property-fallbacks"></target>
